gw.api.web.team

Interface PCTeamModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    TeamModel
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PCDefaultTeamModel, PCFederatedTeamModel
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PCFederatedRootTeamModel, PCRootTeamModel

    public interface PCTeamModel
extends TeamModel
    Everything that PCF may need to know about the data PCTeamModel refers to is available through these methods. Basic display information (like Label). Actual data (like Activities) is defined in appropriate child interfaces and implemented in PCxxxTeamData
